N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5102.4 - Photographing

State Regulations

Each applicant or licensee shall submit with their
license application a color photograph in the format required by the license
application and that was taken within six months of the date the application is
submitted to the commission. Notes
